{
  "stem": "11175.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They couldn't get into that camp, and they were shot them outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before them they-- they took out just the young boys to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was now a liquidation that said that police, the-- the-- the judenrat had to give them a certain amount of people in this and this time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If not, they have to pay some contra-- some contraband for the Germans, if they would not give them to the amount of people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They tried to get it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They catch the young boys-- and the police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they send them away to somewhere in Lublin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The liquidation was one time, that's right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Liquidation was one time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remained there in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the liquidation, I remained in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had some people came back, and they heard it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We start to hear about Treblinka that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We heard from before then some people they are taking the Treblinka, and the Treblinka is the place where they are liquidate them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't believe in anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're not going to the east to work, because it's not a working place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is just a liquidation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, that first group, which they took away from Otwock, they took into Treblinka and they selected some of the more-- the carpenters, the [INAUDIBLE], and they start to build another-- another part of Treblinka, which they were there.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from them, you know, we found it out, because there was then there is another Treblinka where they burned the people, they killed the people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they said, the other Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't get-- be fooled, they said, because we are working in this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they are-- I knew some people, when I got there, which they built that Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
